name: Black and Cream Beauty
description:
Beautiful simple design, black and cream cotton, with a detachable cream bow, fully lined with inside and outside pocket... 

Two poppers to close the bag, quite possibly the most elegant and simple design ever! 

Size 13 1/2width x 11 1/2 height inches

name: Sexy black and gold detachable bow bag
description: Beautiful handmade bag, handles cross over so that you can wear it on your forearm or shoulder. Made from heavy black cotton, golden lining with matching detachable bow - which can double up as a scarf (if you wish!)Finish to an extremely high standard and is perfect for that 'something special!'

name: Sunny Delight
description:
Look at this amazing colour! How bright and breezy is this? I absolutely loved it and what I have created from it...

Beautiful thick yellow-golden cotton fabric, fully lined with inside pocket. Interfaced for that structured look. Super stylish bag with bronze buttons to give a simple yet classic look, hmmmm lovely!

Size: Width13 1/2 x Height 17inches

name: Golden Clutch
description:
Sunny delight in a smaller version! Cute clutch bag same design as the flower fairies, the closing is under the button via a popper. Fully lined with a dark blue thick fabric... Ideal for all those Christmas parties coming up.. Nice one

Size Width 9 x Height 5 1/2inches

name: Flower fairies clutch
description:
Cute floral clutch bag fully lined in cream cotton. It has a delightful and unique tie to do up, a perfect compliment to a slylish gal! 

Size Width 9 x Height 5 1/2inches
